# §5 KDE Plasma Desktop Environment (package-manifest.md §5)
# Debian Stable (trixie) / Plasma 6 substitutions:
# `plasma-workspace-wayland` does NOT exist in current Debian Stable: the Wayland session
#   is part of `plasma-workspace` itself in Plasma 6. Verified via madison.
# `khotkeys` was REMOVED in Plasma 6 (custom shortcuts moved into KDE's
#   built-in global-accel system). Omitted to avoid a missing-package build failure.
plasma-desktop
plasma-workspace
plasma-nm
plasma-pa
kscreen
powerdevil
kde-style-breeze
bluedevil
kde-inotify-survey
